  "description": "These are our current recommendation for mainstream desktop personal computers that offer the best combination of price, value, and longevity is: \u2022 Microprocessor: Pentium 4 at 2.4 GHz (533 MHz front-side bus) \u2022 Memory: 256 MB DDR SDRAM (minimum) \u2022 Hard Drive: 7200 RPM 20 GB or better. (We price 40 GB for consistency) \u2022 Optical: CD-ROM \u2022 Floppy: Optional. (We favor USB flash memory drives in 2003) \u2022 Monitor: 15\" or 17\" XGA-resolution LCD flat panel \u2022 Communications: 1",
